Pacsafe

Pacsafe® bags are all constructed with anti-theft straps, cables, locks and stainless steel wire mesh embedded in the fabric so whether you are traveling around the world or sitting at a café two blocks from home, your Pacsafe® bag will keep all your possessions safe. Featuring slashproof, snatchproof and tamperproof technology, Pacafe® bags offer peace of mind so you can rest comfortably knowing you have your own personal, portable vault.
